# FVWM Config
# Adam Miezianko <adam@theorylounge.org>

DesktopSize 2x2
DesktopName 0 Main
EdgeScroll 100 100
EdgeResistance 350 350
EdgeThickness 1

# Number of miliseconds not to be exceeded to be a click (rather than hold)
ClickTime 350

# Number of pixels the mouse must move to be considered a move.
MoveThreshold 3

Emulate MWM
Style * SloppyFocus
Style * MwmDecor

Colorset 1 fg white, bg #007ab7
Colorset 2 fg white, bg #333333

DestroyDecor MyDecor
AddToDecor MyDecor
+ TitleStyle CenterJustified Height 18
+ ButtonStyle All -- UseTitleStyle

Style "*" UseDecor MyDecor
Style "*" MWMBorder
Style "*" Colorset 2
Style "*" HilightColorset 1

